        {
            "title": "中國股市收跌0.19%，創業板指錄得4連跌！分析師：A股進入 「垃圾時間」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Nvib4xSMzsyQIvZwgu7Dkw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAAG092_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com - </strong>周二，4月28日，A股三大指數低開低走，創業板指、深成指、科創50指數均跌超1%，創業板指日線錄得4連跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今日市場跌多升少，全市場超1600只個股上升，超3600只下跌。滬深兩市成交額2.54萬億，較上一個交易日縮量531億。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至收市，上證綜合指數收跌0.19%，報4078.64點，深證成份指數收跌1.1%，報14830.46點，創業板指數（價格）收跌1.43%，報3596.71點，中國A50期貨指數截稿前升0.08%，報15538點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b670c224-eb75-38b5-93af-2a5986ed0a04-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/POz0itC2wyE_z6NXXBJSMg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://d55-invdn-com.investing.com/content/db09b60ab54ad24da40b770aef0a73fb.png\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">盤面上，工業氣體概念反復活躍，水發燃氣7天6板，蜀道裝備20CM升停。綠電概念快速拉升，華電能源4連板，華銀電力升停，華電遼能觸及升停。醫藥板塊表現活躍，藥明康得、潤都股份、漢森製藥、津藥藥業升停。算力租賃概念盤中走強，群興玩具、三人行、利通電子升停。算力晶片概念延續強勢，綜藝股份4天3板，仁東控股升停。煤炭板塊震盪走高，昊華能源4天2板。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">下跌方面，有色金屬板塊震盪走弱，南山鋁業觸及跌停，錫業股份、株冶集團、赤峰黃金等紛紛下挫。人形機器人概念股多數走低，駿亞科技、捷昌驅動、聯創電子等股跌停。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">巨豐投顧郭一鳴指出，市場正逐步步入一段典型的「垃圾時間」。所謂「垃圾時間」，是指在一段時期內，指數上下兩難、成交趨於清淡、熱點快速輪動而無持續性，導致短線交易價值顯著降低的階段。究其原因，當前時點恰逢4月底這一關鍵視窗期，多重因素疊加壓制了市場的風險偏好。「五一」小長假臨近，假期期間海外市場波動、地緣政治等不確定性因素令資金傾向於持幣過節，規避潛在的黑天鵝事件。短期內市場大概率將維持乏味的震盪磨底格局。</p><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>財報季，美股數字睇到眼花？</span></u></strong> <strong><u><span>Warren AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>一鍵解讀數據！現在</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3dqACWHuQY1UCYQXwJUYQA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://d55-invdn-com.investing.com/content/a5b12b4582bfe9d0a9664d5fa1db03c1.png\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><span><br/></span> <br/></strong></p></blockquote></div>",
