        {
            "title": "美伊談判陷入僵局油價攀升 歐洲股市下滑",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/b7pGX_jRvlBj1RZwXkgzMA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEF030BG_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 歐洲股市週二開盤走低,投資者正在解讀有關美國總統川普可能不願接受伊朗提出的結束兩國兩個月戰爭提議的報導。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間上午03:06(格林威治標準時間07:06),泛歐Stoxx 600指數下跌0.3%,德國Dax指數下滑0.2%,法國CAC 40指數下跌0.3%,英國FTSE 100指數下跌0.1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">媒體報導指出,川普對伊朗最新提議並不滿意。該提議將結束衝突並重新開放荷莫茲海峽,但將有關德黑蘭核武野心的討論推遲到後續階段。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b68bcece-524d-3e79-8020-cf4b6d4cb350-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普經常表示,消除伊朗的核武能力,特別是其獲取核武器的途徑,一直是2月底美以聯合攻擊行動背後的驅動力。路透社援引一位了解此事的美國官員報導稱,正因如此,川普對該提議感到不滿。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊和平談判重啟的希望在週末受挫,當時川普取消派遣談判代表前往巴基斯坦進行新一輪會談。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗外交部長上週末兩次短暫訪問巴基斯坦首都,隨後於週一會見俄羅斯總統普京並獲得其支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在所有外交角力中,荷莫茲海峽仍幾乎對航運交通關閉。這條位於伊朗南部海岸外的狹窄水道是一個關鍵咽喉要道,全球約五分之一的石油經由此處運輸,該水道實際上已關閉數週,支撐油價飆升至遠高於戰前水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場普遍擔憂能源衝擊可能引發全球通脹壓力激增,進而迫使各國央行加息應對。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全球基準布蘭特原油期貨週二再次攀升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個股方面,BP股價上漲。受油氣價格飆升推動,這家英國能源巨頭第一季利潤較去年同期增長逾一倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">挪威航空也因營運虧損低於預期而上漲,部分原因是該公司採取措施對沖不斷上升的航空燃油成本。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">諾華股價下跌,此前這家瑞士製藥商第一季核心營運利潤低於預期。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E9%99%B7%E5%85%A5%E5%83%B5%E5%B1%80%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E6%94%80%E5%8D%87-%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8B%E6%BB%91-082137078.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-28 17:12:15",
