        {
            "title": "Google與五角大樓簽署機密AI協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6_CrUd2j8qGyL_GQv5r0.g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7I0CN_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 據The Information週二報導,引述知情人士消息,Alphabet(NASDAQ:GOOGL)旗下的Google已與美國國防部簽署協議,將其人工智能模型用於機密工作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據The Information報導,該協議允許五角大樓將Google的AI模型用於\"任何合法的政府用途\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">五角大樓此前已與其他主要公司簽署了類似的AI協議,包括OpenAI和xAI,以便在機密環境中使用其模型。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cb86d820-fe69-31a3-88bd-914857012f24-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此前,Claude開發商Anthropic與國防部因在某些軍事和監控應用中使用其AI而發生重大分歧。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華盛頓郵報》週一的報導顯示,數百名Google員工向執行長Sundar Pichai請願,要求拒絕與五角大樓進行機密AI合作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/google%E8%88%87%E4%BA%94%E8%A7%92%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%93%E7%B0%BD%E7%BD%B2%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86ai%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-065402820.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-28 14:59:37",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "大埔火災｜政府收購宏福苑業權 或納入宏志閣 75%業主初步同意",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aNVsF9Qay_.YXI_n011FbQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/ac796713c049dfc2f611a63cb06d7122\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大埔宏福苑火災後，政府早前宣佈將會以收購業權的方式收購宏福苑其中七幢業權，不包括未被大火波及的<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"宏志閣\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:宏志閣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/宏志閣\">宏志閣</a>，除非取得當中大部份業主的共識才會作出考慮。根據本地媒體報道，現時有75%的宏志閣業主同意出售業權，料政府今日下午作出公佈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據政府早前宣佈將會斥資68億元進行收購，當中28億元「大埔宏福苑援助基金」捐款、加上40億元公帑，收購呎價高於測量業界估價三分之一，將以8000元呎價收購未補地價單位；已補地價單位則以10500元呎價收購。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a912bd07-848c-3cad-aeb7-66446412f2c9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於其中的宏志閣未有被大火波及，亦有部份業主表示希望回到原本單位居住，政府原本的方案不打算收購該大廈。但政府亦表示若業主有主流共識，政府才適合啟動探討。若宏志閣最終能達成共識並獲納入方案，收購價將與另外7幢「看齊」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大埔南區議員羅曉楓表示，有收到宏志閣居民反映希望有機會讓政府一併回購他們的單位，因為擔心日後面對單幢屋苑的管理問題，指：「因除咗原有生活環境已經面目全非之外，日夜對住七座已經燒焦嘅大廈，以及日後面對拆樓嘅問題」。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E7%81%AB%E7%81%BD-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC%E5%AE%8F%E7%A6%8F%E8%8B%91%E6%A5%AD%E6%AC%8A-%E6%88%96%E7%B4%8D%E5%85%A5%E5%AE%8F%E5%BF%97%E9%96%A3-75-%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F-063644766.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-28 14:43:44",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日圓在日本央行鷹派維持利率後走強,美元穩定靜待聯準會與伊朗局勢",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Srwy39tTNAblpN40PEJ2MA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEE090L2_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 日圓週二走強,此前日本央行維持利率不變,但因通膨風險上升而暗示未來將升息,而美元則在聯準會會議開始前保持穩定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於美國與伊朗持續僵局的跡象在很大程度上削弱了對風險驅動貨幣的需求,加上油價持續上漲也令市場保持警惕,亞洲其他貨幣大多走弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本週焦點還包括澳洲通膨數據和中國採購經理人指數數據,將於未來幾天公佈。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>日圓在日本央行維持利率並暗示未來升息後小幅走強</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日圓兌美元USD/JPY下跌0.2%,接近跌破159日圓水平,此前日本央行維持利率穩定在0.75%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c5fc942c-fb73-31ec-ab5f-ffde1a9d18e0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但這次維持利率的決定遠非一致,該行九名利率決策委員會成員中有三名呼籲升息。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本央行發出信號表示準備進一步升息,特別是在下調經濟增長預測的同時大幅上調本財年通膨預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該央行預計2026年通膨將遠高於其2%的年度目標,中東戰爭導致的油價衝擊是這一趨勢的主要驅動因素。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Capital Economics分析師表示,日本央行的鷹派立場使得6月升息25點子的可能性看起來很大。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>亞洲外匯因伊朗不確定性而走弱,美元在聯準會會議前保持穩定</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於伊朗戰爭的不確定性幾乎沒有緩解,亞洲其他貨幣大幅走弱。隔夜報導顯示,美國總統唐納德·川普對伊朗重新開放荷莫茲海峽並結束戰爭的提議不滿意,德黑蘭的核活動仍是主要爭議點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週二油價延續近期漲勢,荷莫茲海峽仍處於關閉狀態。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">亞洲貨幣受到油價上漲和對中東僵局延長的擔憂而受挫。對週二稍後開始的聯準會會議的預期也構成壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數和美元指數期貨在亞洲交易中保持穩定,此前在近期交易中錄得一些漲幅。聯準會被廣泛預期將維持利率不變,這可能是主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾在該央行的最後一次會議,因為他的任期將於5月15日結束。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">焦點還集中在凱文·沃什作為下任聯準會主席的潛在確認上,此前美國高層立法者表示,在司法部撤銷對鮑威爾的調查後,他們將推進他的任命。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在亞洲,對油價敏感的印度盧比USD/INR上漲0.3%,進一步突破94盧比水平,而南韓韓元USD/KRW下跌0.1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳元AUD/USD持平,等待週三公佈的第一季度消費者通膨關鍵數據。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">人民幣USD/CNY上漲0.1%,焦點完全集中在週四公佈的4月份採購經理人指數數據上。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新加坡元USD/SGD持平,而新台幣USD/TWD上漲0.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93%E5%9C%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E9%B7%B9%E6%B4%BE%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%BE%8C%E8%B5%B0%E5%BC%B7-%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A%E9%9D%9C%E5%BE%85%E8%81%AF%E6%BA%96%E6%9C%83%E8%88%87%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2-054741777.html",
